#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:30
msgid "Alas, I die without having avenged Gu."
msgstr "Hélas, je meurs sans avoir vengé Gu."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:44
msgid "I'm glad you didn't let me in the crypt. You must go now. You can't do anything for me anymore. I'm sure you will accomplish great things, even without me."
msgstr "Je suis contente que vous ne m'ayez pas laisser dans la crypte. Vous devez partir maintenant. Vous ne pouvez plus rien faire pour moi. Je suis sûre que vous accomplirez de grandes choses, même sans moi. "

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:61
msgid "You can now longer recruit nor recall Scholars."
msgstr "Vous ne pouvez plus recruter ou rappeller des Initiés"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:73
msgid "I'm sorry. You'll have to find another travel leader."
msgstr "Je suis désolé. Vous allez devoir trouver un nouveau chef de voyage."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:90
msgid "You can now longer recruit nor recall sergeants."
msgstr "Vous ne pouvez plus recrutez ou rappeller des sergents."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:102
msgid "I hope not to have been rude or deceiving."
msgstr "J'espère n'avoir pas été grossière ou décevante."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:106
msgid "I knew I hadn't totally recovered from my injuries..."
msgstr "Je savais que je n'avais pas totalement récupéré de mes blessures..."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:110
msgid "Maybe if I had trained before you came, I would have been able to stay with you."
msgstr "Peut-être que si je m'étais entrainée avant que vous n'arriviez, j'aurais été capable de rester avec vous."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:114
msgid "Be careful."
msgstr "Faites attention à vous."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:137
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:384
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:474
msgid "You can now longer recruit nor recall bowmen."
msgstr "Vous ne pouvez plus recruter ou rappeller des archers."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:151
msgid "I don’t know what you think but I think this is where we part."
msgstr "Je ne sais pas ce que vous en pensez mais je pense que c'est là que nous nous séparons."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:155
msgid "Good luck anyway."
msgstr "Bonne chance dans tous les cas."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:172
msgid "You can now longer recruit nor recall Fencers."
msgstr "Vous ne pouvez plus recruter ou rappeller des bretteurs. "

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:185
msgid "That's how you thank me for having saved your life?"
msgstr "C'est ainsi que vous me remerciez d'avoir sauvé votre vie ?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:189
msgid "You won't go far without me."
msgstr "Vous n'irez pas loin sans moi."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:206
msgid "You can now longer recruit nor recall dwarvish fighters."
msgstr "Vous ne pouvez plus recruter ou rappeller des guerriers nains."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:219
msgid "I good friend, break enemies until dead. "
msgstr "Moi bon ami, casse ennemis jusqu'à morts."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:223
msgid "You walk a bit, think with head. "
msgstr "Vous marcher un peu, penser avec tête."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:227
msgid "You like Uwiu. But Uwiu dead."
msgstr "Vous apprécier Uwiu. Mais Uwiu mort."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:244
msgid "You can now longer recruit nor recall bandits."
msgstr "Vous ne pouvez plus recrutez ou rappeller des bandits."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:257
msgid "Just my luck! One more that didn't like mages!"
msgstr "Juste ma chance ! Encore un qui n'aimait pas les mages !"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:261
msgid "Well, let me tell we don't eat children, we don't make milk go sour and we don't turn people into toads..."
msgstr "Et bien, laissez moi dire que nous ne mangeons pas les enfants, que nous ne faisons pas tourner le lait et que nous ne transformons pas les gens en crapauds..."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:265
msgid "And believe me, I regret it right now."
msgstr "Et croyez moi, je le regrette maintenant."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:288
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:434
msgid "You can now longer recruit nor recall Mages."
msgstr "Vous ne pouvez plus recruter ou rappeller des mages."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:303
msgid "How?"
msgstr "Comment ?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:307
msgid "You dare treating the great mage of the 10th legion, third in line for the throne, like that? "
msgstr "Vous osez traiter le grand mage de la 10ème légion, troisième dans l'ordre de succession au trône, comme ça ?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:311
msgid "I hope you don’t wish doing anything else than selling mule shit, because this is all you will be able to expect doing after today. "
msgstr "J'espère que vous ne souhaitez pas faire autre chose que vendre du crottin de mule, car c'est tout ce que vous pourrez espérer faire après aujourd'hui."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:315
msgid "I am gone."
msgstr "Je pars."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:338
msgid "You can now longer recruit nor recall mages."
msgstr "Vous ne pouvez plus recruter ou rappeller des mages."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:353
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:449
msgid "This may be better for you. "
msgstr "C'est peut-être mieux pour vous."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:357
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:453
msgid "I had my objective, but it seems yours is different. "
msgstr "J'avais mon objectif, mais les vôtres semblent différents."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:361
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:457
msgid "It is better that we split."
msgstr "C'est mieux que nous nous séparions."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:399
msgid "In the name of Of, you can’t be serious!  "
msgstr "Au nom d'Of, vous ne pouvez pas être sérieux ! "

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:403
msgid "I haven't last an hour here!"
msgstr "Je n'ai pas tenu une heure ici !"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:407
msgid "Say, you won’t abandon me, will you? "
msgstr "Dites, vous ne m'abandonnerez pas, n'est-ce pas ?"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:411
msgid "My skull would not survive, I know it."
msgstr "Mon crâne ne surviverait pas, je le sais."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:487
msgid "If you have been happy, zo is Ubidaiubua. "
msgstr "Si vous zavez zété content, Ubidaiubua auzzi."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:491
msgid "Fdi’s Travelerz will never thank you enough."
msgstr "Les Voyageurs de Fdi ne vous remerzierons jamais zazzez. "

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:508
msgid "You can now longer recruit nor recall red mages."
msgstr "Vous ne pouvez plus recrutez ou rappeller des mages rouges"

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:521
msgid "Poor horse."
msgstr "Pauvre cheval. "

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:531
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/global_events.cfg:560
msgid "I am afraid we will have to leave most of the food here."
msgstr "J'ai bien peur qu'on doivent laisser la pluaprt de la nourriture ici."

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/deaths.cfg:535
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/global_events.cfg:564
msgid "We need to find a way to carry food and some of it as soon as possible, or we will starve to death."
msgstr "On doit trouver de quoi transporter de la nourriture ainsi que de la nourriture au plus tôt, ou on va mourir de faim. "

