msgstr "Tuve suficiente áspero."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7617
msgid "A basic morion made of steel."
msgstr "Un morrión básico hecho de acero."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7620
msgid "Ripper morion with visor of the fox"
msgstr "Morrión rasgador con visera del zorro"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7636
msgid "Did I rip people off?"
msgstr "¿Rasgué a la gente?"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7651
msgid "A fox should not be of the jury at a goose's trial."
msgstr "Un zorro no debería ser del jurado en el juicio de un ganso."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7666
msgid "For when times get rough."
msgstr "Para cuando los tiempos se ponen ásperos."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7680
msgid "The first thing we're gonna do out there is to rip down that bloody flag on our land."
msgstr "Lo primero que haremos allá afuera es rasgar esa maldita bandera en nuestra tierra."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7693
msgid "Indifference to style is almost always symptomatic of the dogmatic sclerosis of content."
msgstr "La indiferencia al estilo es casi siempre sintomática de la esclerosis dogmática del contenido."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7708
msgid "The government mistakenly attributed the attacks to separatists."
msgstr "El gobierno atribuyó erróneamente los ataques a separatistas."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7721
msgid "Nature plays tricks."
msgstr "La naturaleza juega trucos."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7734
msgid "Every increase of needs increases existential fear."
msgstr "Cada aumento de necesidades aumenta el miedo existencial."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7750
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7768
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 57 %</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 24 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 57 %</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. disminuidos en 24 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7783
msgid "To shoot far, you need to curve the trajectory."
msgstr "Para disparar lejos, necesitan curvar la trayectoria."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7786
msgid "Slippery short reinforced bow of revival"
msgstr "Arco corto reforzado resbaladizo de resurrección"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7800
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 57 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 1</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 7 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 57 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 1</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. disminuidos en 7 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7803
msgid "So slippery that the fear’s as bad as falling."
msgstr "Tan resbaladizo que el miedo es tan malo como caer."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7820
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 42 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 1</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 7 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 42 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 1</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. disminuidos en 7 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7823
msgid "Many things are preferable when not slippery. But not this one."
msgstr "Muchas cosas son preferibles cuando no son resbaladizas. Pero no esta."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7836
msgid "There's not a lot of detail about when the initial patient returning to Idaamub became symptomatic."
msgstr "No hay mucho detalle sobre cuándo el paciente inicial regresando a Idaamub se volvió sintomático."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7849
msgid "Let not politicians and racist demagogues rip asunder."
msgstr "Que no políticos y demagogos racistas rasguen asunder."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7862
msgid "He ripped on him!"
msgstr "¡Lo rasgó!"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7865
msgid "Burning ripper greatsword"
msgstr "Gran espada rasgadora ardiente"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7876
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9127
msgid "We want an iota of power over the things that ripped our lives apart at the seams."
msgstr "Queremos un iota de poder sobre las cosas que rasgaron nuestras vidas en las costuras."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7889
msgid "Grandeur of ideas is precision of ideas."
msgstr "La grandeza de las ideas es precisión de ideas."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7904
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 40 %</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 7 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 40 %</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. disminuidos en 7 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7907
msgid "You will be later revived."
msgstr "Serán revividos más tarde."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7920
msgid "Wilt thou destroy all the city for lack of five?"
msgstr "¿Destruirás toda la ciudad por falta de cinco?"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7936
msgid "I'll rip your soul out!"
msgstr "¡Rasgaré su alma!"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7949
msgid "It has seen a lot of battles."
msgstr "Ha visto muchas batallas."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7961
msgid "Be careful not to cut you."
msgstr "Tengan cuidado de no cortarse."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7978
msgid "You should be put on notice that ripping off homeowners won’t be tolerated."
msgstr "Deben saber que rasgar a dueños de casas no será tolerado."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7981
msgid "Ripper spiked mace of revival"
msgstr "Maza con púas rasgadora de revival"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7991
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 33 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 1</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 7 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 33 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 1</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. disminuidos en 7 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:7998
msgid "Says this to him, who proceeds to rip an orc's spine out."
msgstr "Dice esto a él, quien procede a rasgar la espina de un orco."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8012
msgid "Four years ago my partner - my friend - was killed and I took about as much revenge as any man can take."
msgstr "Hace cuatro años mi pareja - mi amigo - fue asesinado y tomé tanta venganza como cualquier hombre puede tomar."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8028
msgid ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Increases physical resistances by 3%</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Chance to get hit decreased by 20%</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 7 HP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Aumenta resistencias físicas en 3%</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Chance de ser golpeado disminuida en 20%</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máx. aumentados en 7 PV.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8031
msgid "Like a great rough diamond, it may do very well in a closet by way of curiosity, and also for its intrinsic value; but it will never be worn, nor shine, if it is not polished."
msgstr "Como un gran diamante áspero, puede servir muy bien en un armario por curiosidad, y también por su valor intrínseco; pero nunca se usará, ni brillará, si no se pule."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8043
msgid "Hide behind it if needed."
msgstr "Escóndanse detrás si es necesario."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8055
msgid "Negative represents opposites."
msgstr "Negativo representa opuestos."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8058
msgid "Aggressive wooden shield of the fox"
msgstr "Escudo de madera agresivo del zorro"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8073
msgid "This will not stand, this aggression against us."
msgstr "Esto no se mantendrá, esta agresión contra nosotros."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8089
msgid "Allow to recruit Ice Troll Heroes"
msgstr "Permet de recruter des Héros Troll des Glaces"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8090
msgid "Ugh! Agh!"
msgstr "¡Ugh! ¡Agh!"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8132
msgid "Allow to recruit Ghosts"
msgstr "Permet de recruter des Fantômes"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8133
msgid "Come to me, you who are dead!"
msgstr "¡Vengan a mí, ustedes que están muertos!"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8136
msgid "Stingy tails"
msgstr "Colas tacañas"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8149
msgid "Allow to recruit Giant Scorpions"
msgstr "Permet de recruter des Scorpions Géants"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8150
msgid "If they are surrounded by fire, they will suicide by stinging themselves."
msgstr "Si están rodeados por fuego, se suicidarán picándose a sí mismos."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8153
msgid "Wool morion of the fox"
msgstr "Morrión de lana del zorro"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8168
msgid "To make women learned, and foxes tame, hath the same operation, which teacheth them to steale more cuningly."
msgstr "Hacer mujeres eruditas, y zorros mansos, tiene la misma operación, que les enseña a robar más astutamente."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8171
msgid "Ring of the skunk"
msgstr "Anillo del zorrillo"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8182
msgid "Your chickens are all safe; thar's two of them skunks I killed!"
msgstr "Sus pollos están todos a salvo; ¡hay dos de esos zorrillos que maté!"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8185
msgid "Brand new quarterstaff of massacre"
msgstr "Bastón de cuarto nuevo de masacre"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8203
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 52 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 1</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 3 HP.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 6 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 52 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 1</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máx. aumentados en 3 PV.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. disminuidos en 6 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8208
msgid "Ready to spill blood."
msgstr "Listo para derramar sangre."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8211
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8213
msgid "700 gold"
msgstr "700 de oro"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8219
msgid "Jewelry accounts for over 50 percent of the world’s gold demand."
msgstr "La joyería representa más del 50 por ciento de la demanda de oro del mundo."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8222
msgid "Incantation of experience"
msgstr "Encantación de experiencia"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8235
msgid "Will slowly turn HP in XP."
msgstr "Transforme petit à petit les PV en XP."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8236
msgid "This is what you get from spending to much time inside"
msgstr "Esto es lo que obtienen de pasar demasiado tiempo adentro"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8239
msgid "Scale boots of inversion"
msgstr "Botas de escamas de inversión"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8253
msgid "A clever jig of inversion."
msgstr "Un jig astuto de inversión."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8256
msgid "Steel sword"
msgstr "Espada de acero"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8265
msgid "A good sword made of steel."
msgstr "Una buena espada hecha de acero."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8268
msgid "Short sword"
msgstr "Espada corta"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8277
msgid "A short sword made to be light."
msgstr "Una espada corta hecha para ser ligera."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8280
msgid "Slippery cloak"
msgstr "Capa resbaladiza"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8293
msgid "Give me any slippery stuff like philosophy or sociology to tie things up with."
msgstr "Dame cualquier cosa resbaladiza como filosofía o sociología para atar las cosas."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8296
msgid "Burning ripper hammer"
msgstr "Martillo rasgador ardiente"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8307
msgid "It'll rip your lungs out!"
msgstr "¡Rasgará sus pulmones!"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8310
msgid "Heating shield"
msgstr "Escudo calefactor"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8319
msgid "A shield with an inner layer of fur for cold winters."
msgstr "Un escudo con una capa interna de piel para inviernos fríos."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8322
msgid "Aggressive metal targe"
msgstr "Targa de metal agresiva"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8333
msgid "The vast majority of the peoples of the world are against war and against aggression. Not me."
msgstr "La gran mayoría de los pueblos del mundo están en contra de la guerra y contra la agresión. Yo no."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8336
msgid "Great troll axe"
msgstr "Gran hacha de troll"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8346
msgid "One need to be high and strong as a troll to use it properly."
msgstr "Uno necesita ser alto y fuerte como un troll para usarla correctamente."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8349
msgid "Rough bliaut of the fox"
msgstr "Bliaut áspero del zorro"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8365
msgid "The crooked shall be made straight, and the rough places plain."
msgstr "Lo torcido se enderezará, y los lugares ásperos se allanarán."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8377
msgid "Does anyone pretend that preparation for resistance to aggression is unleashing war?"
msgstr "¿Alguien pretende que la preparación para la resistencia a la agresión es desatar la guerra?"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8389
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11174
msgid "This outburst is extreme!"
msgstr "¡Este estallido es extremo!"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8392
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12474
msgid "Ripper blade-staff"
msgstr "Bastón con hoja rasgador"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8403
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11244
msgid "I just wanted to rip him apart."
msgstr "Solo quería rasgarlo en pedazos."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8406
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8408
msgid "500 gold"
msgstr "500 de oro"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8414
msgid "Gold from industrial mines may be exported directly to refiners, while artisanal gold may pass from one trader to another before being exported for refining."
msgstr "El oro de minas industriales puede exportarse directamente a refinadores, mientras que el oro artesanal puede pasar de un comerciante a otro antes de exportarse para refinación."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8417
msgid "Ripper Olaf's helm"
msgstr "Casco de Olaf rasgador"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8426
msgid "He'll rip your lungs out, Jim!"
msgstr "¡Rasgará tus pulmones, Jim!"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8429
msgid "Cloak of vivacity"
msgstr "Capa de vivacidad"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8442
msgid "Let us learn from the lips of death the lessons of vivacity."
msgstr "Aprendamos de los labios de la muerte las lecciones de vivacidad."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8445
msgid "Persevering turtle shield"
msgstr "Escudo de tortuga perseverante"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8464
msgid "Just remember, you can do anything you set your mind to, but it takes action, perseverance, and facing your fears."
msgstr "Solo recuerden, pueden hacer cualquier cosa que se propongan, pero toma acción, perseverancia y enfrentar sus miedos."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8467
msgid "Leather gloves of the fox"
msgstr "Guantes de cuero del zorro"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8478
msgid "The foxes have holes, and the birds of the air have nests; but the Son of man hath not where to lay his head."
msgstr "Los zorros tienen madrigueras, y las aves del cielo tienen nidos; pero el Hijo del hombre no tiene dónde recostar la cabeza."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8481
msgid "Leather gloves of vivacity"
msgstr "Guantes de cuero de vivacidad"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8489
msgid "One day, I'm going to find a man who thinks I'm the meaning of vivacity."
msgstr "Un día, encontraré un hombre que piense que soy el significado de vivacidad."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8492
msgid "Scale boots"
msgstr "Botas de escamas"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8500
msgid "Are those giant snake or dragon scales?"
msgstr "¿Esas son escamas de serpiente gigante o dragón?"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8503
msgid "Ripper staff of precision"
msgstr "Bastón rasgador de precisión"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8514
msgid "Just because we rip on you for being rich doesn't mean we don't like you."
msgstr "Solo porque les rasgamos por ser ricos no significa que no nos gusten."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8517
msgid "Avenging short reinforced bow"
msgstr "Arco corto reforzado vengador"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8528
msgid "There is no revenge so complete as forgiveness."
msgstr "No hay venganza tan completa como el perdón."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8531
msgid "Slippery twisted short bow"
msgstr "Arco corto retorcido resbaladizo"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8541
msgid ""
"And he that stands upon a slippery place\n"
"Makes nice of no vile hold to stay him up."
msgstr ""
"Y el que está en un lugar resbaladizo\n"
"No hace asco de ninguna sujeción vil para sostenerse."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8545
msgid "Rough scale armor"
msgstr "Armadura de escamas áspera"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8553
msgid "The scales are rough but they are strong."
msgstr "Las escamas son ásperas pero son fuertes."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8558
msgid "Some food"
msgstr "Algo de comida"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8563
msgid "It fills up the belly."
msgstr "Llena la barriga."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8566
msgid "Rough metal targe"
msgstr "Targa de metal áspero"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8575
msgid "Who knows, it might be a diamond in the rough."
msgstr "Quién sabe, podría ser un diamante en bruto."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8578
msgid "Slippery mail gloves"
msgstr "Guantes de malla resbaladizos"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8587
msgid "I see how slippery things can be."
msgstr "Veo cuán resbaladizas pueden ser las cosas."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8590
msgid "Rough Olaf's helm"
msgstr "Casco áspero de Olaf"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8598
msgid "Jaunppy used to say to Olaf the philosopher, who was rough and morose, ``Good Olaf, sacrifice to the Graces.''"
msgstr "Jaunppy solía decir a Olaf el filósofo, que era áspero y moroso, «Buen Olaf, sacrifica a las Gracias.»"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8601
msgid "Greatsword of vivacity"
msgstr "Gran espada de vivacidad"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8611
msgid "Karma is the Law of Cause and Effect as applied to the vivacity of the soul."
msgstr "El karma es la Ley de Causa y Efecto aplicada a la vivacidad del alma."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8614
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8616
msgid "1000 gold"
msgstr "1000 de oro"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8622
msgid "Gold refiners play a crucial role in the gold supply chain."
msgstr "Los refinadores de oro juegan un rol crucial en la cadena de suministro de oro."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8625
msgid "Severe cuir-bouilli greaves of vivacity"
msgstr "Grebas de cuero hervido severas de vivacidad"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8633
msgid "This is unpleasantly rough, severe and cruel."
msgstr "Esto es desagradablemente áspero, severo y cruel."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8636
msgid "Tree mace"
msgstr "Maza de árbol"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8645
msgid "Just a big branch."
msgstr "Solo una gran rama."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8648
msgid "Long bow"
msgstr "Arco largo"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8658
msgid "To shoot far."
msgstr "Para disparar lejos."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8661
msgid "Twisted morion"
msgstr "Morrión retorcido"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8672
msgid "More aerodynamic than your usual morion."
msgstr "Más aerodinámico que su morrión usual."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8675
msgid "Heavy wooden targe of the fox"
msgstr "Targa de madera pesada del zorro"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8689
msgid "Whence do you have it that the terrestrial globe is so heavy?"
msgstr "¿De dónde lo tienen que el globo terrestre es tan pesado?"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8707
msgid ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Increases physical resistances by 1%</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistance to arcane increased by 5%</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 10 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Aumenta resistencias físicas en 1%</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistencia a arcano aumentada en 5%</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. disminuidos en 10 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8710
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11321
msgid "An example of severe sadness is depression."
msgstr "Un ejemplo de tristeza severa es la depresión."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8721
msgid "These rough notes and their dead bodies must tell the tale."
msgstr "Estas notas ásperas y sus cuerpos muertos deben contar la historia."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8733
msgid "We find something about all our friends to rip on."
msgstr "Encontramos algo sobre todos nuestros amigos para rasgar."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8755
msgid ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Increases physical resistances by 1%</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistance to arcane increased by 5%</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 5 HP.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP increased by 4 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Aumenta resistencias físicas en 1%</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistencia a arcano aumentada en 5%</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máx. aumentados en 5 PV.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. aumentados en 4 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8759
msgid "A storm strongly imply severe and dangerous weather."
msgstr "Una tormenta implica fuertemente clima severo y peligroso."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8775
msgid "The new psychology must inevitably be built upon the premise that this one vivacity is not man's sole opportunity in which to achieve integration and eventual perfection."
msgstr "La nueva psicología debe inevitablemente construirse sobre la premisa de que esta única vivacidad no es la sola oportunidad del hombre para lograr integración y eventual perfección."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8794
msgid "All rough and politics."
msgstr "Todo áspero y política."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8805
msgid "Mail is light, so I can put more of it."
msgstr "La malla es ligera, así que puedo poner más de ella."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8821
msgid "No organic craftsman, however brilliant, understands the detailed working of the human mind or body very well. "
msgstr "Ningún artesano orgánico, por brillante que sea, entiende muy bien el trabajo detallado de la mente o el cuerpo humano."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8836
msgid "I have enough rough."
msgstr "Tengo suficiente áspero."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8851
msgid ""
"<span color='orange'>This unit's health is restored by 250 HP.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>This unit's experience is increased by 25 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='orange'>La salud de esta unidad se restaura en 250 PV.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>La experiencia de esta unidad se aumenta en 25 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8874
msgid "Refuge is where the heart is."
msgstr "El refugio es donde está el corazón."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8890
msgid "Your wife rips down the steps!"
msgstr "¡Su esposa rasga los pasos!"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8905
msgid "Join the company of foxes rather than assume the lead among lions."
msgstr "Únete a la compañía de zorros en lugar de asumir el liderazgo entre leones."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8920
msgid "O world, thy slippery turns!"
msgstr "¡Oh mundo, tus giros resbaladizos!"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8935
msgid "Universal peace is declared and the foxes have a sincere interest in prolonging the lives of the poultry."
msgstr "La paz universal se declara y los zorros tienen un interés sincero en prolongar las vidas de las aves de corral."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8946
msgid "Red is faster."
msgstr "Rojo es más rápido."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8961
msgid "Like a great rough diamond, it may do very well in a closet by way of curiosity."
msgstr "Como un gran diamante áspero, puede servir muy bien en un armario por curiosidad."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8976
msgid "A prince must imitate the fox and the lion."
msgstr "Un príncipe debe imitar al zorro y al león."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:8992
msgid "The criticism should not be fully reasoned, analytical or convincing, but rough, bureaucratic, metaphysical and dogmatic."
msgstr "La crítica no debería ser completamente razonada, analítica o convincente, sino áspera, burocrática, metafísica y dogmática."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9004
msgid "The plain places shall be made rough"
msgstr "Los lugares llanos se harán ásperos"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9020
msgid "The fox can defend himself from wolves"
msgstr "El zorro puede defenderse de los lobos"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9033
msgid "And then you come over and rip the steps down!"
msgstr "¡Y luego vienen y rasgan los pasos!"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9049
msgid "One must be a fox to recognize traps."
msgstr "Uno debe ser un zorro para reconocer trampas."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9068
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 12 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 1</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Chance to get hit decreased by 5%</span> \n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 10 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 12 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 1</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Chance de ser golpeado disminuida en 5%</span> \n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. disminuidos en 10 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9072
msgid "I am accustomed to pay men back in their own coin."
msgstr "Estoy acostumbrado a pagar a los hombres con su propia moneda."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9085
msgid "Ouch, that pricks!"
msgstr "¡Ay, eso pincha!"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9100
msgid "Women do most delight in revenge."
msgstr "Las mujeres se deleitan más en la venganza."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9113
msgid "A triumph on slippery slopes of syntax."
msgstr "Un triunfo en pendientes resbaladizas de sintaxis."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9139
msgid "It has seen better days, but it is as heavy as new."
msgstr "Ha visto mejores días, pero es tan pesado como nuevo."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9151
msgid "With a non-cutting side to block the enemy sword."
msgstr "Con un lado no cortante para bloquear la espada enemiga."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9165
msgid "It's a slippery slope."
msgstr "Es una pendiente resbaladiza."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9179
msgid "O scaly, slippery, wet, swift, staring wights, what is 't ye do?"
msgstr "Oh escamosos, resbaladizos, húmedos, rápidos, mirones blancos, ¿qué hacen?"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9196
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 57 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 2</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 7 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 57 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 2</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. disminuidos en 7 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9199
msgid "Give them slippery stuffs like philosophy or sociology to tie things up with."
msgstr "Denles cosas resbaladizas como filosofía o sociología para atar las cosas."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9212
msgid "The good seed that nature plants in us is so slight and so slippery that it cannot withstand the least harm from wrong nourishment."
msgstr "La buena semilla que la naturaleza planta en nosotros es tan ligera y tan resbaladiza que no puede resistir el menor daño de una nutrición equivocada."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9225
msgid "Vivacity hath more awe than death."
msgstr "La vivacidad tiene más temor que la muerte."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9228
msgid "Avenging mace of focus"
msgstr "Maza vengadora de enfoque"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9242
msgid "Revenge is better than power."
msgstr "La venganza es mejor que el poder."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9257
msgid "Revenge is a dead thing, reaching out from the past to grasp you."
msgstr "La venganza es una cosa muerta, extendiéndose desde el pasado para agarrarlos."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9274
msgid "You will catch the fox with cunning."
msgstr "Atraparán al zorro con astucia."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9287
msgid "It used to belong to a carpenter."
msgstr "Solía pertenecer a un carpintero."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9300
msgid "Better than a branch."
msgstr "Mejor que una rama."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9313
msgid "On the slippery slope of treason?"
msgstr "¿En la pendiente resbaladiza de traición?"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9327
msgid "It all started when some forward-thinking people launched a group that would rip the lid off guild and government wrongdoing to animals."
msgstr "Todo empezó cuando algunas personas con pensamiento adelantado lanzaron un grupo que rasgaría la tapa de los errores del gremio y gobierno a animales."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9340
msgid "Charge!"
msgstr "¡Carga!"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9354
msgid "Sweet is revenge."
msgstr "Dulce es la venganza."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9371
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 76 %</span>\n"
"<span color='red'>50% fewer attacks</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 7 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado un 76 %</span>\n"
"<span color='red'>50 % menos ataques</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>PX máximo reducido en 7 PX.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9374
msgid ""
" I have said before\n"
"That the past experience revived in the meaning\n"
"Is not the experience of one life only\n"
"But of many generations — not forgetting\n"
"Something that is probably quite ineffable."
msgstr ""
" Lo he dicho antes\n"
"Que la experiencia pasada revivida en el significado\n"
"No es la experiencia de una vida solo\n"
"Sino de muchas generaciones — no olvidando\n"
"Algo que probablemente es bastante inefable."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9393
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 39 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 1</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 12 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 39 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 1</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. disminuidos en 12 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9397
msgid "Damn, it's too bad that nobody is here to see this sweet rip."
msgstr "Maldición, es una lástima que nadie esté aquí para ver este dulce rasgado."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9413
msgid "Allow to recruit Shadows"
msgstr "Permet de recruter des Ombres"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9414
msgid ""
"When light came into the world and gave form to the unknown, fear was forced to retreat into darkness. Since that day, the shadows of the world have held terror for humanity, though it knows not why.\n"
"That is a question which is easily answered by a necromancer."
msgstr ""
"Cuando la luz vino al mundo y dio forma a lo desconocido, el miedo fue forzado a retirarse a la oscuridad. Desde ese día, las sombras del mundo han sostenido terror para la humanidad, aunque no sabe por qué.\n"
"Esa es una pregunta que es fácilmente respondida por un nigromante."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9431
msgid "For when you bang your head."
msgstr "Para cuando se golpean la cabeza."

#. [effect]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9444
msgid "ice breath"
msgstr "aliento de hielo"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9537
msgid "Rafanador ed’krilipuk!"
msgstr "¡Rafanador ed’krilipuk!"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9552
msgid "Ooooommmmm."
msgstr "Ooooommmmm."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9572
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9574
msgid "1500 gold"
msgstr "1500 de oro"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9580
msgid "Because the vast majority of the world’s gold passes through a small number of refiners, these companies are sometimes called the “choke point” of the gold supply chain."
msgstr "Porque la gran mayoría del oro del mundo pasa a través de un pequeño número de refinadores, estas compañías a veces se llaman el «punto de estrangulamiento» de la cadena de suministro de oro."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9583
msgid "Organic studded leather boots of the fox"
msgstr "Botas de cuero tachonado orgánico del zorro"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9595
msgid "Part of the charm of synthetic organic craftsmanship derives from the vastness of the intellectual landscape along several dimensions."
msgstr "Parte del encanto de la artesanía orgánica sintética deriva de la vastedad del paisaje intelectual a lo largo de varias dimensiones."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9598
msgid "Ripper finned mace of outburst"
msgstr "Maza rasgadora con aletas de estallido"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9608
msgid "So rip the stage rip the state rip the system, I was born to rage against them."
msgstr "Así que rasga el escenario rasga el estado rasga el sistema, nací para rabiar contra ellos."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9611
msgid "Ripper straight axe of the fox"
msgstr "Hacha recta rasgadora del zorro"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9625
msgid "Uteaqniq Zei, did he rip people off?"
msgstr "Uteaqniq Zei, ¿rasgó a la gente?"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9628
msgid "Medium crossbow of the fox"
msgstr "Ballesta mediana del zorro"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9641
msgid "The King taking a straw from the ground, pardoned the fox of all his trespasses which either he or his father had ever committed."
msgstr "El Rey tomando una paja del suelo, perdonó al zorro de todos sus delitos que él o su padre hubieran cometido alguna vez."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9644
msgid "Hammer of carving"
msgstr "Martillo de tallado"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9653
msgid "I have always preferred direct carving to modelling because I like the resistance of the hard material and feel happier working that way."
msgstr "Siempre he preferido el tallado directo al modelado porque me gusta la resistencia del material duro y me siento más feliz trabajando de esa manera."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9656
msgid "Icicles"
msgstr "Carámbanos"

#. [effect]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9666
msgid "ice shard"
msgstr "fragmento de hielo"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9690
msgid "Also known as the ``Frozen finger of Bitrul''."
msgstr "También conocido como el «Dedo congelado de Bitrul»."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9693
msgid "Unscratched metal targe"
msgstr "Targa de metal sin rasguños"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9703
msgid "We found about a dozen unscratched metal targes."
msgstr "Encontramos alrededor de una docena de targes de metal sin rasguños."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9706
msgid "Rough cuir-bouilli gloves"
msgstr "Guantes de cuero hervido ásperos"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9714
msgid "The road may be rough, but it cannot be long."
msgstr "El camino puede ser áspero, pero no puede ser largo."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9717
msgid "Rough morion with visor"
msgstr "Morrión áspero con visera"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9729
msgid "Lays the rough paths of peevish Nature even, And opens in each heart a little heaven."
msgstr "Allana los caminos ásperos de la Naturaleza caprichosa, Y abre en cada corazón un pequeño cielo."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9732
msgid "Precision"
msgstr "Precisión"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9745
msgid "This unit rallies the adjacent allies to better dodge, decreasing their chance to be hit by 20%."
msgstr "Esta unidad reúne a los aliados adyacentes para esquivar mejor, disminuyendo su chance de ser golpeados en 20%."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9748
msgid "Great helm of the fox"
msgstr "Gran casco del zorro"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9760
msgid " If the fox now began to smile, it was no wonder."
msgstr " Si el zorro ahora comenzaba a sonreír, no era de extrañar."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9763
msgid "Woven morion"
msgstr "Morrión tejido"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9774
msgid "Woven by old ladies."
msgstr "Tejido por señoras mayores."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9777
msgid "Wooden targe of vivacity"
msgstr "Targa de madera de vivacidad"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9786
msgid "Vivacity! we've been long together."
msgstr "¡Vivacidad! hemos estado mucho tiempo juntos."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9789
msgid "Brigandine gloves"
msgstr "Guantes de brigandina"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9800
msgid "Cloak of the fox"
msgstr "Capa del zorro"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9816
msgid "The fox has many tricks, the hedgehog only one."
msgstr "El zorro tiene muchos trucos, el erizo solo uno."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9819
msgid "Scimitar"
msgstr "Cimitarra"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9828
msgid "With a convex curved blade, good for slashing opponents while riding on a horse."
msgstr "Con una hoja curva convexa, buena para cortar oponentes mientras montan a caballo."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9831
msgid "Bow of disease"
msgstr "Arco de enfermedad"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9840
msgid "Only in this age and generation is it at last possible to indicate the causes of those diseases which today devastate the human frame."
msgstr "Solo en esta era y generación es posible por fin indicar las causas de esas enfermedades que hoy devastan el marco humano."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9843
msgid "Gem morion of the fox"
msgstr "Morrión de gema del zorro"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9854
msgid "Tar-baby ain't sayin' nuthin', en brer Fox, he lay low."
msgstr "Tar-baby no dice nada, en brer Fox, se queda bajo."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9857
msgid "Avenging scale boots"
msgstr "Botas de escamas vengadoras"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9870
msgid "Revenge is like a ghost."
msgstr "La venganza es como un fantasma."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9873
msgid "Leather boots of monstrosity"
msgstr "Botas de cuero de monstruosidad"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9883
msgid "In comparison such a monstrosity as phlegm for flem is merely disgusting."
msgstr "En comparación tal monstruosidad como flema para flem es meramente asquerosa."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9886
msgid "Ripper sharp battle-axe"
msgstr "Hacha de batalla afilada rasgadora"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9897
msgid "What history and the free choices of people have joined together, let not politicians and demagogues rip asunder."
msgstr "Lo que la historia y las elecciones libres de la gente han unido, que no políticos y demagogos rasguen asunder."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9900
msgid "Ripper spikes mace of outburst"
msgstr "Maza de púas rasgadora de estallido"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9910
msgid "There will be a whole mess of us laughing and getting stoned on our way to Oof, and the first thing we're gonna do out there is to rip down that bloody flag on the fort."
msgstr "Habrá un montón de nosotros riendo y drogándonos en nuestro camino a Oof, y lo primero que haremos allá es rasgar esa maldita bandera en el fuerte."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9913
msgid "Shiny hamstring cutter"
msgstr "Cortador de tendones brillante"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9933
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11227
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 57 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 1</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 5 HP.</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Increases physical resistances by 1%</span> \n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 9 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 57 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 1</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máx. aumentados en 5 PV.</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Aumenta resistencias físicas en 1%</span> \n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. disminuidos en 9 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9938
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11232
msgid "How about a shiny pair of handcuffs instead?"
msgstr "¿Qué tal un par de esposas brillantes en su lugar?"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9941
msgid "Midnight spikes mace"
msgstr "Maza de púas de medianoche"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9953
msgid "That hour o' night's black arch the keystane."
msgstr "Esa hora del arco negro de la noche la piedra angular."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9956
msgid "Fire breath"
msgstr "Aliento de fuego"

#. [effect]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:9966
msgid "flame"
msgstr "llama"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10028
msgid "Nork’Tarrh ed’krilipuk!!"
msgstr "¡¡Nork’Tarrh ed’krilipuk!!"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10031
msgid "Light boots"
msgstr "Botas ligeras"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10038
msgid "A pair of boots made out of fabric."
msgstr "Un par de botas hechas de tela."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10041
msgid "Scale gloves of the fox"
msgstr "Guantes de escamas del zorro"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10053
msgid "Take us the foxes, the little foxes, that spoil the vines."
msgstr "Tómanos los zorros, los pequeños zorros, que estropean las viñas."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10056
msgid "Blade-staff"
msgstr "Bastón con hoja"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10066
msgid "For those who cannot choose between mage and warrior."
msgstr "Para aquellos que no pueden elegir entre mago y guerrero."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10069
msgid "Distinct hamstring cutter"
msgstr "Cortador de tendones distinto"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10089
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 57 %</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 5 HP.</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Increases physical resistances by 1%</span> \n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistance to pierce increased by 3%.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 7 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 57 %</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máx. aumentados en 5 PV.</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Aumenta resistencias físicas en 1%</span> \n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistencia a perforación aumentada en 3%.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. disminuidos en 7 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10094
msgid "Even among those who reject the supposed superiority of a particular species over any other, the perception of distinct, genetically determined species persists."
msgstr "Incluso entre quienes rechazan la supuesta superioridad de una especie particular sobre cualquier otra, persiste la percepción de especies distintas determinadas genéticamente."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10097
msgid "Slippery bow of increase"
msgstr "Arco resbaladizo de aumento"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10108
msgid "One steps onto a slippery slope whenever analysis moves from the descriptive to the historic plane."
msgstr "Uno pisa una pendiente resbaladiza siempre que el análisis se mueve del plano descriptivo al histórico."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10111
msgid "Optimistic slaughtering mallet of promise"
msgstr "Mazo de matanza optimista de promesa"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10132
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 103 %</span>\n"
"<span color='red'>33% fewer attacks</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 4 HP.</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Increases physical resistances by 1%</span> \n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistance to pierce increased by 3%.</span>\n"
"<span color='#C0C000'>New weapon special: mind raid</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Enemy resistance to impact decreased by 1%</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 103 %</span>\n"
"<span color='red'>33% menos ataques</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máx. aumentados en 4 PV.</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Aumenta resistencias físicas en 1%</span> \n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistencia a perforación aumentada en 3%.</span>\n"
"<span color='#C0C000'>Nueva especial de arma: asalto mental</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Resistencia enemiga a impacto disminuida en 1%</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10139
msgid "Optimism is the opposite of pessimism, exemplifies a lifeview where one looks upon the world as a positive place."
msgstr "El optimismo es lo opuesto al pesimismo, ejemplifica una visión de la vida donde uno mira al mundo como un lugar positivo."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10142
msgid "Uncommon astral doublet"
msgstr "Doblete astral poco común"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10165
msgid "I shall emphasize not what is common is us, but what is uncommon, and this leads me to a restatement of the question."
msgstr "Enfatizaré no lo que es común en nosotros, sino lo que es poco común, y esto me lleva a una reformulación de la pregunta."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10168
msgid "Short bow of throw"
msgstr "Arco corto de lanzamiento"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10177
msgid "So doth Of, in Her triumphal ascension into heaven, throw the greatest gifts for the good of men that were ever given."
msgstr "Así hace Of, en Su ascensión triunfal al cielo, lanza los mayores dones para el bien de los hombres que jamás se hayan dado."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10180
msgid "Disgusting coat"
msgstr "Abrigo asqueroso"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10193
msgid "Disgust is one of our most basic emotions."
msgstr "El asco es una de nuestras emociones más básicas."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10196
msgid "Shiny sultan gloves"
msgstr "Guantes de sultán brillantes"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10213
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 1</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 5 HP.</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Increases physical resistances by 3%</span> \n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 9 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 1</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máx. aumentados en 5 PV.</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Aumenta resistencias físicas en 3%</span> \n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. disminuidos en 9 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10217
msgid "If you say: they're shiny, nice, new gloves, then you're wrong from current moment's point of view, because the gloves are not yet like that."
msgstr "Si dicen: son guantes brillantes, lindos, nuevos, entonces están equivocados desde el punto de vista del momento actual, porque los guantes aún no son así."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10220
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10222
msgid "2000 gold"
msgstr "2000 de oro"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10228
msgid "Around the world, millions of people work in gold and diamond mining."
msgstr "Alrededor del mundo, millones de personas trabajan en minería de oro y diamantes."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10231
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10233
msgid "3000 gold"
msgstr "3000 de oro"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10239
msgid ""
"Bright El Dorado, land of gold,\n"
"We have so sought for thee,\n"
"There's not a spot in all the globe\n"
"Where such a land can be. "
msgstr ""
"Brillante El Dorado, tierra de oro,\n"
"Tanto te hemos buscado,\n"
"No hay un lugar en todo el globo\n"
"Donde tal tierra pueda ser."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10245
msgid "Medium slippery crossbow of design"
msgstr "Ballesta mediana resbaladiza de diseño"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10256
msgid "I don't see crossbow as a slippery slope down to people marrying snakes."
msgstr "No veo la ballesta como una pendiente resbaladiza hacia gente casándose con serpientes."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10259
msgid "Distinct animal-skin boots"
msgstr "Botas de piel de animal distintas"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10272
msgid ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Increases physical resistances by 2%.</span>\n"
"        <span color='#60A0FF'>Resistance to pierce increased by 3%.</span>\n"
"        <span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 5 HP.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 7 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Aumenta resistencias físicas en 2%.</span>\n"
"        <span color='#60A0FF'>Resistencia a perforación aumentada en 3%.</span>\n"
"        <span color='orange'>PV máx. aumentados en 5 PV.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. disminuidos en 7 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10280
msgid "I am known for my influential arguments for substance dualism, where mind and body are considered to have distinct essences, one being characterized by thought, the other by spatial extension."
msgstr "Soy conocido por mis argumentos influyentes para el dualismo de sustancia, donde mente y cuerpo se consideran tener esencias distintas, una caracterizada por el pensamiento, la otra por extensión espacial."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10291
msgid "The diamond in the rough."
msgstr "El diamante en bruto."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10294
msgid "Rough thin morion"
msgstr "Morrión delgado áspero"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10302
msgid "Choose always the way that seems the best, however rough it may be."
msgstr "Elige siempre el camino que parezca el mejor, por áspero que sea."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10305
msgid "Swamp mace"
msgstr "Maza de pantano"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10314
msgid "Just a big root."
msgstr "Solo una gran raíz."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10317
msgid "Mail gloves of the fox"
msgstr "Guantes de malla del zorro"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10329
msgid "As sheepish as a fox captured by a fowl."
msgstr "Tan tímido como un zorro capturado por un ave."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10332
msgid "Aggressive wool morion"
msgstr "Morrión de lana agresivo"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10346
msgid "We need the swift gathering of forces to confront not only military but moral aggression."
msgstr "Necesitamos la rápida reunión de fuerzas para confrontar no solo agresión militar sino moral."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10349
msgid "Unscratched heating shield of refuge"
msgstr "Escudo calefactor sin rasguños de refugio"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10363
msgid ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Increases physical resistances by 2%.</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Chance to get hit decreased by 20%</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistance to pierce increased by 3%.</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 5 HP.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP increased by 4 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Aumenta resistencias físicas en 2%.</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Chance de ser golpeado disminuida en 20%</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistencia a perforación aumentada en 3%.</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máx. aumentados en 5 PV.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. aumentados en 4 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10372
msgid "Each year, millions of people enter the sea and come out unscratched and unscathed and oblivious to the notion that they’ve had a wilderness experience."
msgstr "Cada año, millones de personas entran al mar y salen sin rasguños e ilesos y ajenos a la noción de que han tenido una experiencia de desierto."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10375
msgid "Slippery cloak of the fox"
msgstr "Capa resbaladiza del zorro"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10392
msgid "Magic makes for a slippery concept."
msgstr "La magia hace un concepto resbaladizo."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10395
msgid "Slippery great claymore"
msgstr "Gran claymore resbaladiza"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10405
msgid "Love is a slippery game."
msgstr "El amor es un juego resbaladizo."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10408
msgid "Shiny slippery bow"
msgstr "Arco brillante resbaladizo"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10422
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 53%</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 1</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Increases physical resistances by 1%.</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 5 HP.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 9 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 53%</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 1</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Aumenta resistencias físicas en 1%.</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máx. aumentados en 5 PV.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. disminuidos en 9 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10432
msgid "Don't judge the future of a person based on his present conditions, because time has the power to change black coal to shiny diamond."
msgstr "No juzguen el futuro de una persona basado en sus condiciones presentes, porque el tiempo tiene el poder de cambiar carbón negro a diamante brillante."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10435
msgid "Ripper cloak of the fox"
msgstr "Capa rasgadora del zorro"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10452
msgid "Criminals should be put on notice that ripping off homeowners and taxpayers won’t be tolerated."
msgstr "Los criminales deben saber que rasgar a dueños de casas y contribuyentes no será tolerado."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10455
msgid "Avenging war bow"
msgstr "Arco de guerra vengador"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10466
msgid "You know what they say about revenge? You better be ready to dig two graves."
msgstr "¿Saben lo que dicen sobre la venganza? Mejor estén listos para cavar dos tumbas."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10469
msgid "Studded leather gloves of awareness"
msgstr "Guantes de cuero tachonado de conciencia"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10477
msgid ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Increases physical resistances by 1%.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 10 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Aumenta resistencias físicas en 1%.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. disminuidos en 10 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10483
msgid "Every individual is at once the beneficiary and the victim of the linguistic tradition into which he has been born — the beneficiary inasmuch as language gives access to the accumulated records of other people's experience, the victim in so far as it confirms him in the belief that reduced awareness is the only awareness and as it bedevils his sense of reality, so that he is all too apt to take his concepts for data, his words for actual things."
msgstr "Cada individuo es a la vez el beneficiario y la víctima de la tradición lingüística en la que ha nacido — el beneficiario en tanto que el lenguaje da acceso a los registros acumulados de la experiencia de otras personas, la víctima en tanto que lo confirma en la creencia de que la conciencia reducida es la única conciencia y como embruja su sentido de la realidad, de modo que es muy apto para tomar sus conceptos por datos, sus palabras por cosas reales."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10486
msgid "Cloth of boldness"
msgstr "Tela de audacia"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10499
msgid "Boldness, more boldness, always boldness."
msgstr "Audacia, más audacia, siempre audacia."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10502
msgid "Sharp staff"
msgstr "Bastón afilado"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10512
msgid "Be careful not to hurt yourself."
msgstr "Tengan cuidado de no herirse."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10515
msgid "Knife-staff"
msgstr "Bastón-cuchillo"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10525
msgid "A bit better than just sticking a knife a each end of a staff."
msgstr "Un poco mejor que solo pegar un cuchillo en cada extremo de un bastón."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10528
msgid "Ripper blade-staff of increase"
msgstr "Bastón con hoja rasgador de aumento"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10540
msgid "The strategy is to let the virus rip through the population, infecting up to 40 million people, most of whom will recover and then be immune to the virus."
msgstr "La estrategia es dejar que el virus rasgue a través de la población, infectando hasta 40 millones de personas, la mayoría de las cuales se recuperarán y luego serán inmunes al virus."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10543
msgid "War bow of revival"
msgstr "Arco de guerra de revival"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10551
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 75%</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 7 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 75%</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. disminuidos en 7 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10558
msgid ""
"When thy flowery hand delivers\n"
"All the mountain-prisoned rivers,\n"
"And thy great heart beats and quivers,\n"
"To revive the days that were."
msgstr ""
"Cuando tu mano florida entrega\n"
"Todos los ríos prisioneros de la montaña,\n"
"Y tu gran corazón late y tiembla,\n"
"Para revivir los días que fueron."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10564
msgid "Shiny bow of destruction"
msgstr "Arco brillante de destrucción"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10578
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 51%</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 1</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Increases physical resistances by 1%.</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 5 HP.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 9 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 51%</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 1</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Aumenta resistencias físicas en 1%.</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máx. aumentados en 5 PV.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. disminuidos en 9 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10588
msgid "I always wanted to be one of the shiny, happy people."
msgstr "Siempre quise ser uno de la gente brillante y feliz."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10591
msgid "Cuir-bouilli greaves of the fox"
msgstr "Grebas de cuero hervido del zorro"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10603
msgid "Where the lion's skin falls short it must be eked out with the fox's."
msgstr "Donde la piel del león falla corta debe ser alargada con la del zorro."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10606
msgid "Gnarled staff"
msgstr "Bastón nudoso"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10616
msgid "The gnarl makes it stronger."
msgstr "El nudo lo hace más fuerte."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10619
msgid "Coat of awareness"
msgstr "Abrigo de conciencia"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10631
msgid ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Increases physical resistances by 5%.</span>\n"
"<span color='#FF99CC'>1 extra movement point</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 40 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Aumenta resistencias físicas en 5%.</span>\n"
"<span color='#FF99CC'>1 punto de movimiento extra</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. disminuidos en 40 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10638
msgid "Let yourself really become aware"
msgstr "Déjense realmente volverse conscientes"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10641
msgid "Ring of the dog"
msgstr "Anillo del perro"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10652
msgid "Who let the dogs out?"
msgstr "¿Quién dejó salir a los perros?"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10655
msgid "Terracotta helm"
msgstr "Casco de terracota"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10663
msgid "It should protect your head at least once."
msgstr "Debería proteger su cabeza al menos una vez."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10666
msgid "Aggressive linen cloth of the fox"
msgstr "Tela de lino agresiva del zorro"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10684
msgid "Every general reprisal is a hostile aggression."
msgstr "Toda represalia general es una agresión hostil."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10687
msgid "Rigid chainmail"
msgstr "Cota de malla rígida"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10695
msgid "Why use small rings when you can have big ones."
msgstr "Por qué usar anillos pequeños cuando pueden tener grandes."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10710
msgid "We carry faithfully what one gives us to bear, on hard shoulders and over rough mountains."
msgstr "Llevamos fielmente lo que uno nos da para cargar, en hombros duros y sobre montañas ásperas."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10713
msgid "Rough cuir-bouilli gauntlets of the fox"
msgstr "Guanteletes de cuero hervido ásperos del zorro"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10725
msgid "Is it a hot-house plant, which must be framed and glassed, lest March, that bold young fellow, should shake the life out of it in his rough play among the flowers?"
msgstr "¿Es una planta de invernadero, que debe enmarcarse y vidriarse, no sea que Marzo, ese joven audaz, sacuda la vida de ella en su juego áspero entre las flores?"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10728
msgid "Medium crossbow"
msgstr "Ballesta mediana"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10737
msgid "Faster than any bow."
msgstr "Más rápida que cualquier arco."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10740
msgid "Rusty assault axe"
msgstr "Hacha de asalto oxidada"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10750
msgid "Rusty from the blood of the enemies."
msgstr "Oxidada por la sangre de los enemigos."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10753
msgid "Blunt assault axe"
msgstr "Hacha de asalto desafilada"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10763
msgid "Blunt from smashing to many helms."
msgstr "Desafilada por aplastar demasiados cascos."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10766
msgid "Club of monstrosity"
msgstr "Garrote de monstruosidad"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10778
msgid "This monstrosity is the manifestation of the very weakness within me that I've been running from my entire life. "
msgstr "Esta monstruosidad es la manifestación de la debilidad misma dentro de mí de la que he estado huyendo toda mi vida."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10781
msgid "High-calibre slippery war bow"
msgstr "Arco de guerra resbaladizo de alto calibre"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10791
msgid "I'm a slippery kipper with a brain to match."
msgstr "Soy un arenque resbaladizo con un cerebro a juego."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10794
msgid "Ripper staff of boldness"
msgstr "Bastón rasgador de audacia"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10805
msgid "My traps rips out ribcages seconds later."
msgstr "Mis trampas rasgan cajas torácicas segundos después."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10808
msgid "Ripper blade-staff of outburst"
msgstr "Bastón con hoja rasgador de estallido"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10819
msgid "I proceed to rip their spines out."
msgstr "Procedo a rasgar sus espinas."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10822
msgid "Organic ring"
msgstr "Anillo orgánico"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10830
msgid "There is a vast body of organic reactions that serve to transform one substance into another."
msgstr "Hay un vasto cuerpo de reacciones orgánicas que sirven para transformar una sustancia en otra."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10833
msgid "Unscratched cloak"
msgstr "Capa sin rasguños"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10846
msgid "It was left unscratched."
msgstr "Fue dejado sin rasguños."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10849
msgid "Dress of awareness"
msgstr "Vestido de conciencia"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10861
msgid ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Increases physical resistances by 6%</span>\n"
"<span color='#FF99CC'>1 extra movement point</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 10 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Aumenta resistencias físicas en 6%</span>\n"
"<span color='#FF99CC'>1 punto de movimiento extra</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. disminuidos en 10 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10868
msgid "The objection I have repeatedly made privately against those who ordinarily proclaim believes in religions is that they, themselves surrounded and safeguarded by all too many illusions, do not have the courage to make people aware."
msgstr "La objeción que he hecho repetidamente en privado contra aquellos que ordinariamente proclaman creencias en religiones es que ellos, rodeados y salvaguardados por demasiadas ilusiones, no tienen el coraje de hacer consciente a la gente."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10871
msgid "Ripper staff of conflict"
msgstr "Bastón rasgador de conflicto"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10883
msgid "I'll rip your lungs out!"
msgstr "¡Rasgaré sus pulmones!"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10886
msgid "Avenging mace of boldness"
msgstr "Maza vengadora de audacia"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10897
msgid "Doubtless, revenge is not always sweet, once it is consummated we feel inferior to our victim, or else we are tangled in the subtleties of remorse."
msgstr "Sin duda, la venganza no siempre es dulce, una vez consumada nos sentimos inferiores a nuestra víctima, o estamos enredados en las sutilezas del remordimiento."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10900
msgid "Blade-staff of conflict"
msgstr "Bastón con hoja de conflicto"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10912
msgid "Conflict will never be eliminated from human affairs."
msgstr "El conflicto nunca será eliminado de los asuntos humanos."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10915
msgid "Mail boots of the inversion"
msgstr "Botas de malla de inversión"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10929
msgid "He thought that his move would rescue the theory of linear progress from the absurdities of the old inversion theory."
msgstr "Pensó que su movimiento rescataría la teoría del progreso lineal de las absurdidades de la vieja teoría de inversión."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10943
msgid "As I, jump on stage, flip rip a show."
msgstr "Como yo, salto al escenario, giro rasgo un show."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10946
msgid "Short crossbow"
msgstr "Ballesta corta"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10955
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11003
msgid "A basic crossbow."
msgstr "Una ballesta básica."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10958
msgid "Young wood halberd"
msgstr "Alabarda de madera joven"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10970
msgid "Fragile crossbow"
msgstr "Ballesta frágil"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10982
msgid "Damaged halberd"
msgstr "Alabarda dañada"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:10994
msgid "Crossbow"
msgstr "Ballesta"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11006
msgid "Short slippery crossbow of increase"
msgstr "Ballesta corta resbaladiza de aumento"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11020
msgid "Damaged crossbow"
msgstr "Ballesta dañada"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11032
msgid "Halberd of vivacity"
msgstr "Alabarda de vivacidad"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11045
msgid "Long farmer's crossbow"
msgstr "Ballesta larga de granjero"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11058
msgid "Curved halberd"
msgstr "Alabarda curva"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11070
msgid "Infallible brillant curved crossbow"
msgstr "Ballesta curva brillante infalible"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11094
msgid "This crossbow has to be thought of as infallible."
msgstr "Esta ballesta debe pensarse como infalible."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11097
msgid " Cruel optimistic halberd of promise"
msgstr "Alabarda cruel optimista de promesa"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11117
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 36 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 1</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 4 HP.</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Increases physical resistances by 1%</span> \n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistance to pierce increased by 3%.</span>\n"
"<span color='#C0C000'>New weapon special: mind raid</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Enemy resistance to blade decreased by 1%</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 36 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 1</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máx. aumentados en 4 PV.</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Aumenta resistencias físicas en 1%</span> \n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistencia a perforación aumentada en 3%.</span>\n"
"<span color='#C0C000'>Nueva especial de arma: asalto mental</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Resistencia enemiga a hoja disminuida en 1%</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11127
msgid "Weakened war crossbow"
msgstr "Ballesta de guerra debilitada"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11136
msgid "It used to be a good crossbow. Used to."
msgstr "Solía ser una buena ballesta. Solía."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11139
msgid "Avenging halberd"
msgstr "Alabarda vengadora"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11153
msgid "High-calibre crossbow"
msgstr "Ballesta de alto calibre"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11162
msgid "Having well polished the whole crossbow, he added a golden tip."
msgstr "Habiendo pulido bien toda la ballesta, añadió una punta dorada."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11165
msgid "Halberd of outburst"
msgstr "Alabarda de estallido"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11177
msgid "Crossbow of revival"
msgstr "Ballesta de revival"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11195
msgid "Ripper halberd"
msgstr "Alabarda rasgadora"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11208
msgid "Shiny halberd"
msgstr "Alabarda brillante"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11235
msgid "Ripper thin chainmail"
msgstr "Cota de malla delgada rasgadora"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11259
msgid "I divide the world into hedgehogs and foxes."
msgstr "Divido el mundo en erizos y zorros."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11278
msgid "This master by his rough theories of revolutionary tactics has contributed most to form the discipline, energy and power of the cohorts. "
msgstr "Este maestro por sus teorías ásperas de tácticas revolucionarias ha contribuido más a formar la disciplina, energía y poder de las cohortes."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11298
msgid "The first issue was rushed by horse across pavements slippery with mud and rain to a waiting express cart, reserved especially for the occasion."
msgstr "El primer número fue llevado a caballo a través de pavimentos resbaladizos con lodo y lluvia a un carro expreso esperando, reservado especialmente para la ocasión."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11312
msgid ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Increases physical resistances by 2%</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistance to fire increased by 5%</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistance to cold increased by 5%</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistance to arcane increased by 5%</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 10 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Aumenta resistencias físicas en 2%</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistencia a fuego aumentada en 5%</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistencia a frío aumentada en 5%</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistencia a arcano aumentada en 5%</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. disminuidos en 10 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11324
msgid "Ripper studded leather gloves of inversion"
msgstr "Guantes de cuero tachonado rasgadores de inversión"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11339
msgid "I used to kill pigeons, rip their heads off, 'You dirty rat pigeon!'."
msgstr "Solía matar palomas, rasgar sus cabezas, «¡Tú sucia rata paloma!»."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11351
msgid "Vivacity has compensations, but there’s no way of knowing what they are."
msgstr "La vivacidad tiene compensaciones, pero no hay manera de saber qué son."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11369
msgid " Truly, society is like a large piece of frozen water ; there are the rough places to be shunned, the very slippery ones all ready for a fall, and the holes which seem made expressly to drown you."
msgstr " Verdaderamente, la sociedad es como un gran pedazo de agua congelada; hay lugares ásperos que evitar, los muy resbaladizos listos para una caída, y los agujeros que parecen hechos expresamente para ahogarlos."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11384
msgid "The steersman's part is vigilance, Blow it or rough or smooth."
msgstr "La parte del timonel es vigilancia, Sopla o áspero o suave."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11399
msgid ""
"There are, to whom my satire seems too bold;\n"
"Scarce to wise Peter complaisant enough,\n"
"And something said of Udxatfe much too rough."
msgstr ""
"Hay, para quienes mi sátira parece demasiado audaz;\n"
"Apenas complaciente suficiente para el sabio Peter,\n"
"Y algo dicho de Udxatfe mucho demasiado áspero."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11413
msgid "Science leads to great achievements, which, quite rightly, fill of joy those who seek the truth, but if pursued, teaches us that we must seek other sources of ultimate truth and find answers to existential questions about the meaning of vivacity and the mystery of death. "
msgstr "La ciencia lleva a grandes logros, que, con razón, llenan de alegría a aquellos que buscan la verdad, pero si se persigue, nos enseña que debemos buscar otras fuentes de verdad última y encontrar respuestas a preguntas existenciales sobre el significado de la vivacidad y el misterio de la muerte."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11429
msgid ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Increases physical resistances by 1%</span> \n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistance to pierce increased by 4%.</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 5 HP.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP increased by 4 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Aumenta resistencias físicas en 1%</span> \n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistencia a perforación aumentada en 4%.</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máx. aumentados en 5 PV.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. aumentados en 4 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11437
msgid "I think your sister's got a better chance of getting your cart home unscratched than you do."
msgstr "Creo que su hermana tiene mejor chance de llevar su carro a casa sin rasguños que ustedes."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11448
msgid "Bands make one seem thinner."
msgstr "Las bandas hacen que uno parezca más delgado."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11463
msgid "See, he's a salt-of-the-earth guy, and the University nerds don't understand his salt-of-the-earth way, his rough-and-tumble ways."
msgstr "Mira, es un tipo sal de la tierra, y los nerds de la Universidad no entienden su manera sal de la tierra, sus maneras ásperas y tumultuosas."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11479
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11757
msgid "Rip it free!"
msgstr "¡Rasguenlo libre!"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11499
msgid "To my delight, I discovered that fascinating combination of rigor/hypothesis, hard-core theory/intuition, and commercial-level practicality/artistic elegance known as organic craftsmanship in a course at the University."
msgstr "Para mi deleite, descubrí esa fascinante combinación de rigor/hipótesis, teoría dura/intuición, y practicidad a nivel comercial/elegancia artística conocida como artesanía orgánica en un curso en la Universidad."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11514
msgid "I have for a long time been of opinion that the quantity of noise anyone can comfortably endure is in inverse proportion to his mental powers, and may therefore be regarded as a rough estimate of them."
msgstr "Hace mucho tiempo soy de la opinión de que la cantidad de ruido que cualquiera puede soportar cómodamente es en proporción inversa a sus poderes mentales, y por lo tanto puede considerarse como una estimación áspera de ellos."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11517
msgid "Aggressive metal targe of the fox"
msgstr "Targa de metal agresiva del zorro"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11532
msgid "If thou wert the lion, the fox would beguile thee; if thou wert the lamb, the fox would eat thee; if thou wert the fox, the lion would suspect thee, when, peradventure, thou wert accused by the ass..."
msgstr "Si fueras el león, el zorro te engañaría; si fueras el cordero, el zorro te comería; si fueras el zorro, el león te sospecharía, cuando, por aventura, fueras acusado por el asno..."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11551
msgid "Being able to illustrate those experiences for listeners was a triumph, because it took everything to resist all the urges I have as a human being to present myself as good, or healed, or unscratched."
msgstr "Poder ilustrar esas experiencias para los oyentes fue un triunfo, porque tomó todo para resistir todos los impulsos que tengo como ser humano para presentarme como bueno, o sanado, o sin rasguños."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11570
msgid ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Increases physical resistances by 3%.</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Chance to get hit decreased by 14%</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistance to cold increased by 5%.</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistance to fire increased by 5%.</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistance to arcane increased by 5%.</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 5 HP.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP increased by 4 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Aumenta resistencias físicas en 3%.</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Chance de ser golpeado disminuida en 14%</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistencia a frío aumentada en 5%.</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistencia a fuego aumentada en 5%.</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Resistencia a arcano aumentada en 5%.</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máx. aumentados en 5 PV.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. aumentados en 4 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11581
msgid "He drove the merchants from the Temple, and all his severe accusations against the scribes and Pharisees..."
msgstr "Expulsó a los mercaderes del Templo, y todas sus acusaciones severas contra los escribas y fariseos..."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11593
msgid "If positive represents movement to the right, negative represents movement to the left."
msgstr "Si lo positivo representa movimiento hacia la derecha, lo negativo representa movimiento hacia la izquierda."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11596
msgid "Ripper battle-axe of trickery"
msgstr "Hacha de batalla destripadora del engaño"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11608
msgid "He tearfully addressed the troops and, ripping open his tunic to expose his breast, begged them to stand faithfully by him."
msgstr "Con lágrimas en los ojos se dirigió a las tropas y, rasgándose la túnica para exponer su pecho, les suplicó que permanecieran fieles a su lado."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11624
msgid "Vengeance too has its venom, though it comes closer to what we are, to what we feel, to the very law of the self."
msgstr "La venganza también tiene su veneno, aunque se acerca más a lo que somos, a lo que sentimos, a la propia ley del yo."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11639
msgid "Vengeance before Divinity!"
msgstr "¡Venganza antes que Divinidad!"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11652
msgid "The blood of the enemies made it rust."
msgstr "La sangre de los enemigos la hizo oxidar."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11666
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:14366
msgid "We have come more and more under the dominance of mechanics and sacrificed living humanity to the dead rhythm of the machine without most of us even being conscious of the monstrosity of the procedure."
msgstr "Hemos caído cada vez más bajo el dominio de la mecánica y hemos sacrificado la humanidad viva al ritmo muerto de la máquina sin que la mayoría siquiera sea consciente de la monstruosidad del procedimiento."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11679
msgid "It’s much more slippery and hard to get your hands on than in other places where it’s more structured and stratified."
msgstr "Es mucho más resbaladizo y difícil de conseguir que en otros lugares donde está más estructurado y estratificado."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11695
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 117 %</span>\n"
"<span color='red'>25% less attacks</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 7 HP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado un 117 %</span>\n"
"<span color='red'>25 % menos ataques</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máximo aumentado en 7 PV.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11699
msgid "A prince being thus obliged to know well how to act as a beast must imitate the fox and the lion, for the lion cannot protect himself from snares, and the fox cannot defend himself from wolves."
msgstr "Un príncipe, al estar obligado a saber bien cómo actuar como bestia, debe imitar al zorro y al león, pues el león no puede protegerse de las trampas y el zorro no puede defenderse de los lobos."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11712
msgid "We had this really terrific volley and I stepped back to get this really terrific shot."
msgstr "Tuvimos esta ráfaga realmente impresionante y me aparté para tomar esta foto realmente impresionante."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11728
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 75 %</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 5 HP.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP increased by 4 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado un 75 %</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máximo aumentado en 5 PV.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>PX máximo aumentado en 4 PX.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11735
msgid "To refuges pervaded by charm, as to works of Art that approach perfection, the more happily constituted minds say 'Yes' without any qualification."
msgstr "A los refugios impregnados de encanto, como a las obras de arte que se acercan a la perfección, las mentes más felizmente constituidas dicen «sí» sin ninguna calificación"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11749
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 86 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 2</span>\n"
"<span color=red>25% less attacks</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 12 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado un 86 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 2</span>\n"
"<span color='red'>25 % menos ataques</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>PX máximo reducido en 12 PX.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11773
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 76 %</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 5 HP.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP increased by 4 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado un 76 %</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máximo aumentado en 5 PV.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>PX máximo aumentado en 4 PX.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11780
msgid "I felt happy, felt I had come to a refuge, because a refuge to people like me is not a place but all places, all places except the one we happen to be in at the moment. "
msgstr "Me sentí feliz, sentí que había llegado a un refugio, porque un refugio para personas como yo no es un lugar, sino todos los lugares, todos los lugares excepto aquel en el que nos encontramos en ese momento."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11796
msgid "I am appalled and saddened by the attack."
msgstr "Estoy horrorizado y entristecido por el ataque."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11812
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 43 %</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 14 HP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado un 43 %</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máximo aumentado en 14 PV.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11814
msgid "One must be a fox to recognise snares, and a lion to frighten wolves."
msgstr "Hay que ser zorro para reconocer trampas y león para asustar a los lobos."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11827
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 86 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 2</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 10 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 86 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 2</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>XP máx. disminuidos en 10 XP.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11835
msgid "Don't rip..."
msgstr "No rasguen..."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11853
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 86 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 1</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Chance to get hit decreased by 5%</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 2 HP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado un 86 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 1</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Probabilidad de ser golpeado reducida un 5 %</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máximo aumentado en 2 PV.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11858
msgid "If you wish for revenge, an equally hard blow will be dealt back to yourself. "
msgstr "Si deseas venganza, un golpe igual de duro te será devuelto a ti mismo."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11873
msgid "How about..."
msgstr "Qué tal..."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11886
msgid ""
"The Spirits of thy Lines infuse a Fire\n"
"Like the Worlds Soul, which makes me thus aspire "
msgstr ""
"Los Espíritus de tus Linajes infunden un Fuego\n"
"Como el Alma del Mundo, que me hace aspirar así"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11902
msgid "I never take vengeance unless I am forced to do so by an oath or in self-protection."
msgstr "Nunca tomo venganza a menos que me vea forzado a hacerlo por un juramento o en defensa propia."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11918
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 93 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 2</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 5 HP.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP increased by 4 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado un 93 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 2</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máximo aumentado en 5 PV.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>PX máximo aumentado en 4 PX.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11927
msgid "When I ripped my pants, I thought that I had everybody by my side, but I went and blew it all sky-high, and now she won't even spare a passing glance, all just because I ripped my pants."
msgstr "Cuando me rasgué los pantalones, pensé que todos estaban de mi lado, pero lo arruiné todo por completo y ahora ni siquiera me dedica una mirada fugaz, todo solo porque me rasgué los pantalones."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11943
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 93 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 1</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 12 HP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado un 93 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 1</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máximo aumentado en 12 PV.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11947
msgid "When big Larry came round just to put him down, Bob turned into a clown, and no girl ever wants to dance with a fool who went and ripped his pants."
msgstr "Cuando el gran Larry llegó solo para derribarlo, Bob se convirtió en payaso, y ninguna chica quiere bailar con un tonto que fue y se rasgó los pantalones."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11960
msgid "Don't miss your chance and you won't end up like the fool who ripped his pants."
msgstr "No desperdicies tu oportunidad y no terminarás como el tonto que se rasgó los pantalones."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11963
msgid "Midnight ripper great claymore"
msgstr "Mandoble destripador de medianoche"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11976
msgid ""
"It was evening here,\n"
"But upon earth the very noon of night."
msgstr ""
"Aquí era de noche,\n"
"pero en la tierra era pleno mediodía de la noche."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11991
msgid "I'm talking about you running through the woods in the snow with blood hounds ripping your clothes off!"
msgstr "¡Estoy hablando de ti corriendo por el bosque en la nieve con sabuesos destrozándote la ropa!"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:11994
msgid "Long slippery crossbow of the fox"
msgstr "Ballesta larga resbaladiza del zorro"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12007
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 93 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 1</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 7 HP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado un 93 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 1</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máximo aumentado en 7 PV.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12011
msgid " I look at it now and it makes all the sense in the world because the whole conversation about race is so disjointed and disconnected, and it’s so hard for us to hold on to it, so it makes sense that a play about something that’s so slippery wouldn’t be in a well-made play structure..."
msgstr "Ahora lo miro y tiene todo el sentido del mundo porque toda la conversación sobre raza está tan fragmentada y desconectada, y nos cuesta tanto aferrarnos a ella, que tiene sentido que una obra sobre algo tan resbaladizo no esté en una estructura de obra bien hecha..."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12024
msgid "The coda of the first movement, with its slippery, chromatic bass and the awesome moans above it, remains a paralyzing experience."
msgstr "El coda del primer movimiento, con su bajo cromático resbaladizo y los gemidos impresionantes por encima, sigue siendo una experiencia paralizante."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12036
msgid "At one hundred yards, volley fire present!"
msgstr "¡A cien yardas, fuego de ráfaga presente!"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12049
msgid "The question is what one makes of these similarities, and one steps onto a slippery slope whenever analysis moves from the descriptive to the historic plane of linguistics."
msgstr "La pregunta es qué se hace con estas similitudes, y uno se adentra en una pendiente resbaladiza cada vez que el análisis pasa del plano descriptivo al histórico de la lingüística"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12062
msgid "The urge for good design is the same as the urge to go on living. "
msgstr "El impulso por un buen diseño es el mismo que el impulso de seguir viviendo."

#. [effect]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12075
msgid "instant lightning"
msgstr "relámpago instantáneo"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12088
msgid "Falash elhre-too!"
msgstr "¡Falash elhre-too!"

#. [effect]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12101
msgid "sparkle rain"
msgstr "lluvia de destellos"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12140
msgid "This unit's and adjacent allie's resistance is increased by 10%."
msgstr "La resistencia de esta unidad y de los aliados adyacentes aumenta un 10 %."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12168
msgid "Adjacent enemies are cursed, dealing 10 less damage and having 10% worse resistances. "
msgstr "Los enemigos adyacentes están malditos, infligen 10 menos de daño y tienen un 10 % peor de resistencias."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12184
msgid "Convert damages taken to lost experience."
msgstr "Convertit les dommages reçus en perte d'XP."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12185
msgid "Allafreth boolk’oh!"
msgstr "¡Allafreth boolk’oh!"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12200
msgid ""
"<span color='orange'>This unit's health is restored by 600 HP.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>This unit's experience is increased by 60 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='orange'>La salud de esta unidad se restaura en 600 PV.</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>La experiencia de esta unidad aumenta en 60 PX.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12204
msgid "Great experience Potion"
msgstr "Gran poción de experiencia"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12215
msgid "<span color='blue'>This unit's experience is increased by 47 XP.</span>"
msgstr "<span color='blue'>La experiencia de esta unidad aumenta en 47 PX.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12218
msgid "Ring of rest"
msgstr "Anillo de reposo"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12229
msgid "<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 7 XP.</span>"
msgstr "<span color='blue'>PX máximo reducido en 7 PX.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12232
msgid "Parade helm"
msgstr "Yelmo de desfile"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12240
msgid "Even better if you're on a horse."
msgstr "Aún mejor si estás a caballo."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12243
msgid "Reinforced short bow of awareness"
msgstr "Arco corto reforzado de consciencia"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12256
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 57 %</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>Max XP decreased by 20 XP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado un 57 %</span>\n"
"<span color='blue'>PX máximo reducido en 20 PX.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12258
msgid "They do not actually risk going out among the people or abandoning illusions in order to make a genuine idea-impression, because they have a dim nothing that it is truly a dangerous matter to make people aware."
msgstr "En realidad no se arriesgan a salir entre la gente ni a abandonar ilusiones para causar una impresión de idea genuina, porque tienen una vaga noción de que es verdaderamente peligroso hacer que la gente tome conciencia."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12261
msgid "Preeminent hamstring cutter"
msgstr "Cortador preeminente de tendones"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12275
msgid "Joyously quivers the air of the hour before dawn, the hour when Of cognized the greatness of Cosmos, and when she prayed in the Garden of Xleyyo."
msgstr "Alegremente vibra el aire de la hora antes del amanecer, la hora en que Of conoció la grandeza del Cosmos y en que ella oró en el Jardín de Xleyyo."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12278
msgid "Avenging winged mace of the fox"
msgstr "Maza alada vengadora del zorro"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12293
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 76 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 1</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Chance to get hit decreased by 5%</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 7 HP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado un 76 %</span>\n"
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 1</span>\n"
"<span color='#60A0FF'>Probabilidad de ser golpeado reducida un 5 %</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máximo aumentado en 7 PV.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12297
msgid "Revenge is the prime ingredient in the fountain of youth. "
msgstr "La venganza es el ingrediente principal de la fuente de la juventud."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12300
msgid "Ripper blade-staff of creation"
msgstr "Cuchilla del Destripador-Bastón de la Creación"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12312
msgid " I think I rather disappointed him by explaining that, no, I certainly *didn't* believe that she had ripped off books of magic, that I doubted she'd read it and that it wouldn't matter if she had."
msgstr "Creo que más bien lo decepcioné al explicarle que no, que ciertamente *no* creía que ella hubiera robado libros de magia, que dudaba que los hubiera leído y que no importaría si lo hubiera hecho."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12315
msgid "Unscratched wooden targe"
msgstr "Adarga de madera sin rasguños"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12325
msgid "It is not designed to eject undamaged compartments."
msgstr "No está diseñada para expulsar compartimentos sin daños."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12328
msgid "Ripper woodman's axe"
msgstr "Hacha destripadora de leñador"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12339
msgid "Believing the first cell originated by chance is like believing a tornado ripping through a junkyard full of wooden parts could produce a cart."
msgstr "Creer que la primera célula surgió por casualidad es como creer que un tornado atravesando un depósito de chatarra lleno de piezas de madera podría producir un carro."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12342
msgid "Linen cloth of vivacity"
msgstr "Tela de lino de vivacidad"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12355
msgid "One's vivacity has value so long as one attributes value to the vivacity of others, by means of love, friendship, indignation and compassion."
msgstr "La vivacidad de uno tiene valor mientras uno atribuya valor a la vivacidad de los demás, mediante el amor, la amistad, la indignación y la compasión."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12358
msgid "Avenging medium crossbow"
msgstr "Ballesta media vengadora"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12369
msgid ""
"To forgive is divine\n"
"But vengeance is mine, mine, mine."
msgstr ""
"Perdonar es divino\n"
"Pero la venganza es mía, mía, mía."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12373
msgid "Hammer of vivacity"
msgstr "Martillo de vivacidad"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12383
msgid "The reincarnation of the human soul is not the introduction of a new principle into evolution, but the adaptation of the universal principle to meet the conditions rendered necessary by the individualization of the continuously evolving vivacity..."
msgstr "La reencarnación del alma humana no es la introducción de un nuevo principio en la evolución, sino la adaptación del principio universal para satisfacer las condiciones hechas necesarias por la individualización de la vivacidad en continua evolución..."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12386
msgid "Aggressive studded leather gloves of vivacity"
msgstr "Guantes de cuero tachonado agresivo de vivacidad"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12397
msgid "There is no motive for aggression."
msgstr "No hay motivo para la agresión."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12400
msgid "Aggressive cloth of inversion"
msgstr "Tela agresiva de inversión"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12420
msgid "The men who are to protect the community against violent aggression easily turn into the most dangerous aggressors."
msgstr "Los hombres que deben proteger a la comunidad contra la agresión violenta fácilmente se convierten en los agresores más peligrosos."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12423
msgid "Rough page's shield of the fox"
msgstr "Escudo tosco de paje del zorro"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12436
msgid "On a very rough-and-ready basis we might define an eccentric as a man who is a law unto himself, and a crank as one who, having determined what the law is, insists on laying it down to others."
msgstr "De manera muy aproximada podríamos definir a un excéntrico como un hombre que es ley en sí mismo, y a un maniático como alguien que, habiendo determinado cuál es la ley, insiste en imponérsela a los demás."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12439
msgid "Ripper spiked mace of vivacity"
msgstr "Maza con púas destripadora de vivacidad"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12450
msgid "It will be a very special pleasure to rip you apart."
msgstr "Será un placer muy especial destrozarte."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12453
msgid "Avenging cloak of the fox"
msgstr "Capa vengadora del zorro"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12471
msgid "They say revenge is empty."
msgstr "Dicen que la venganza es vacía."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12485
msgid "Stare at me in this faceless way, go mad with desire, and rip my clothes off."
msgstr "Mírenme de esta manera sin rostro, enloquezcan de deseo, y rasguen mi ropa."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12488
msgid "Longsword"
msgstr "Espada larga"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12497
msgid "Longer than your arm."
msgstr "Más larga que su brazo."

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12500
msgid "Slippery war bow of the fox"
msgstr "Arco de guerra resbaladizo del zorro"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12513
msgid ""
"<span color='green'>Damage increased by 75 %</span>\n"
"        <span color='green'>Damage increased by 1</span>\n"
"<span color=red>25% less attacks</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>Max HP increased by 2 HP.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 75 %</span>\n"
"        <span color='green'>Daño aumentado en 1</span>\n"
"<span color=red>25% menos ataques</span>\n"
"<span color='orange'>PV máx. aumentados en 2 PV.</span>"

#. [object]
#: Legends_of_Idaamub/utils/item_list.cfg:12518
msgid "There is no ``slippery slope'' toward loss of liberty, only a long staircase where each step down must first be tolerated by the people and their leaders."
msgstr "No hay «pendiente resbaladiza» hacia la pérdida de libertad, solo una larga escalera donde cada paso hacia abajo debe primero ser tolerado por la gente y sus líderes."

